            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Wristbands issued must be utilised on the same day as stated above. The wristband is for per entry usage only and re-entry is not allowed as stated above. No exchange, refund, replacement, or cancellation will be entertained as stated above. No refund will be provided due to ride closures or inclement weather as stated above.Eligibility Free admission applies to children below 90 cm. Child rate applies to children between 90 cm to 130 cm. Adult rate applies to guests with height above 130 cm. Senior guests must present IC at the counter during wristband redemption as stated above.Attraction Access Access is granted upon successful wristband redemption and must follow the above admission and eligibility requirements.Additional Information The Management reserves the right to substitute, amend, or terminate any offers or promotions at any time without prior notice as stated above.Important Notes Guests are required to comply with all above terms and conditions before entry. All policies stated above are subject to change without prior notice."
              }
            ]
